=== Symbols ===

{{multiple image
| perrow=2
| align    = right
| direction =horizontal
| header=Symbols of Ashoka
| total_width=300
| image1   = Sarnath capital.jpg
| caption1 = [[Lion Capital of Ashoka|Ashoka's pillar]] capital of [[Sarnath]]. This sculpture has been adopted as the [[National Emblem of India]].
